disability resources commencment 2012 stanford university skip navigation disability resources chuck painters stanford news service family members and guests with mobility concerns and disabilities are welcome and encouraged to participate in commencement weekend activities please take a moment to review the available accommodations and resources below should you require assistance please complete a request for disability related accomodations by may 25 2012 event accommodations the baccalaureate celebration will be held at the main quadrangle on saturday june 16 at 9 30 am most seating is outside and will be in direct sunlight limited shade is available more info general resources disability parking spaces marked in blue are located throughout the campus these spaces are reserved for vehicles displaying state issued any state disability placards or license plates all others will be cited more info home schedule ceremonies & events information for students parents faculty disability resources getting around traditions more information diversity & access office stanford university mariposa house 585 capistrano way stanford ca 94305 8230 voice 650 725 0326 fax 650 723 1791 disability access stanford edu all special requests for assistance must be made by friday may 25 contact disability resources faq stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
